title: Bitcoin Blockchain 01-01-2016.zip
description:
This is the entire Bitcoin Blockchain as of 01-01-2016. This upload is made to make it more easy to create a full node. 

1) Install Bitcoin XT, BU or even Bitcoin Core. 

2) Don't let your wallet/node sync since that is what this torrent is here to help with. Can easily take days. 

3) Download this torrent and replace "blocks" and "chainstate" with your two folders in your install folder. 

4) Now launch your wallet/node and let it sync the last days since 01-01-2016. 

Any questions or mistakes I made. Find me on reddit.

- /u/FjorXD
